		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Exact cycle timing of PPU internal register copies vs. CPU writes is one thing. Exact cycle timing of mapper IRQ generation or sprite 0 assertion vs. PPU memory accesses is another. Are you talking about sprite 0 splits or MMC3 IRQ splits? How far is your emulator from passing <a href="http://www.slack.net/~ant/nes-tests/" class="postlink">blargg's MMC3 and sprite hit tests</a>?

		

